# Template:
#
#  Rewrite the following expression using only positive exponents.
#
#      x^m 
#    ( --- )^-p
#      y^n
#
# We choose m and n integer on [2,15] and p integer on [2,5].
# 
# Last updated: Carl Yao, 7/03/13
# ENDDESCRIPTION

## DBsubject('Algebra')
